> I've been looking for a replacement camper headliner for a long time:
nothing at the junkyards and what I have has shrunk from the heat and peeled
and is no good. This the vinyl above the cab, the sides and on the bottom on
the top bunk.
>
> GoWesty seems to have started selling a kit.  Does anyone know anything
about it?
